            In this short debate, there has been expressed a general feeling that the arm's length principle should be supported and some disquiet that the clause weakened it. The noble Lord, Lord Chorley, asked a question about that. My noble friend Lord Monro supported the arm's length principle, but the noble Lord, Lord Redesdale, was worried, as was my noble friend Lord Crickhowell.</p><p>
