          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0584P0-05167'>
        <a name='S5LV0584P0_19980122_GCR_119'>  </a>
        <blockquote class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <cite class='member author entry-title unmatched-member'>Lord Howell</cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
